      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1995 Mazda RX-7 FD, maintained to exacting standards. This specimen retains its original 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant, delivering linear boost across the rev range with flawless transition. The chassis exhibits zero fatigue, preserving the legendary 50/50 weight distribution and cornering kinematics provided by its aluminum double-wishbone suspension. Recent compression testing yields optimal, uniform pulses across all rotor faces. The five-speed manual gearbox features crisp gates and healthy synchros, paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Finished in its original paint with an immaculate interior, this FD represents a rare opportunity to own an unmolested example of 90s JDM engineering excellence.",
